# Saving changes when timing out

## STR
* On **edit article page**, make a change
* Wait sufficient time until you have time out
* Click **save* button**
* *Discard changes* popup appears
* user is redirected to login page
* After logging in, user is redirected to **edit article** page
* Unsaved changes are still displayed
* **Save Button** is hidden

## Expected behaviour
* The pop up should read *Your session has timed out. You will be redirected back to this page after you have logged in*
* **Save Button** should not be hidden


